dict.string: A disposition of property for the benefit of some person orpersons, usually through the medium of trustees, and for the benefitof a wife, children, or other relatives; jointure granted to a wife,or the act of granting it.
One of the simplest essential parts, more commonly calledcells, of which animal and vegetable organisms, or their tissues andorgans, are composed.
A suffix composed of -able and the adverbial suffix -ly; as,favorably.

Designating, or pertaining to, a certain class of diseases. SeeZymotic disease, below. Zymotic disease (Med.), any epidemic,endemic, contagious, or sporadic affection which is produced by somemorbific principle or organism acting on the system like a ferment.
